{"id":218232,"type":1,"name":"ラブレター","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b1/ff/218232_0u4ge.jpg","summary":"       成濑真琴是一个非常率真、带点男孩子气的活泼女高中生。在一个偶然的机会下，他遇见了生命中的白马王子──泷泽健一。熟知这个小酷哥竟然是书法界屈指可数的书法大师泷泽先生的独生子。凭着这股对爱情的执着心和超人一等的死缠烂打功夫，真琴决定向未知的书法世界挑战，藉以掳获健一的心。 ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>恋爱青春贴</li><li><span>册数: </span>4</li><li><span>话数: </span>44</li><li><span>作画: </span><a href=\"/person/29620\">若狭たけし</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/6749\">小学館</a>、<a href=\"/person/8365\">時報文化</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/7620\">ビッグコミックスピリッツ</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/9601\">じんのひろあき</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>1997年</li><li><span>结束: </span>1998年</li>","collection":{"collect":2},"tags":[{"name":"若狭たけし","count":1},{"name":"じんのひろあき","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":29620,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/16/5a/29620_prsn_iE6AV.jpg","name":"若狭刚士","desc":"作画"},{"id":6749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/ec/6749_prsn_O9b2I.jpg","name":"小学馆","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8365,"image":"","name":"台湾时报文化","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7620,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a4/33/7620_prsn_I22ua.jpg","name":"周刊BIG COMIC SPIRITS","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":9601,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/25/dd/9601_prsn_DKcv4.jpg","name":"神野浩昌","desc":"原作"}],"comic":[{"id":218228,"name":"ラブレター (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/da/19/218228_jp.jpg"},{"id":218231,"name":"ラブレター (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d3/64/218231_jp.jpg"},{"id":218229,"name":"ラブレター (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1d/e6/218229_jp.jpg"},{"id":218230,"name":"ラブレター (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/06/65/218230_jp.jpg"}]}